Technically, GIA-MY is proficient in **Python** and **JavaScript**, leveraging libraries such as **Pandas**, **Matplotlib**, and **Scikit-learn** for data manipulation, visualization, and machine learning model development. They possess hands-on experience with relational and NoSQL databases including **SQL Server**, **PostgreSQL**, and **MongoDB**. For data visualization and reporting, they are skilled with **Power BI** and **Tableau**, and have experience developing interactive web applications using **Streamlit**. Their toolkit further includes integration capabilities with **Google Sheets API** for dynamic data management. While currently focused on core **Data Analytics** and **Business Intelligence**, their foundational understanding of **Supervised Machine Learning** and **Data Collection** methodologies positions them for growth in advanced analytical roles within retail and customer-centric domains.